id: pm-mu8m
title: "Generate shell completions, MCP tool registrations, and command reference docs from the contracts table (single source of truth)"
description: "Implements grammar principle 6 of the pm-n7rr charter beyond the help tier (pm-e2bq): completions (bash/zsh/fish), the MCP tool table, and command reference doc skeletons become build-time generated from src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts with a CI drift gate, shrinking the ~10-site new-command wiring checklist to ≤3 sites and retiring the recurring contract-drift bug class (pm-zx13, pm-4os2, GH-449). Dedupe-checked 2026-07-06: only pm-e2bq (help tier) exists; no item covers completions/MCP/docs generation."
